    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/42e49649550ac0186ddd2dae9150cff3.poster.avif?t=1761755501\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/42e49649550ac0186ddd2dae9150cff3.webm?t=1761755501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/42e49649550ac0186ddd2dae9150cff3.mp4?t=1761755501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/a24b5803ef82bd7f6879799f43273d70.avif?t=1761755501\" width=365 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Give it your best in the workshop, because here at the <strong>GunShop</strong>, we value every single worker, so get your hands dirty because the spot is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/6903894ef2f6f6daee4eaac2a44944de.poster.avif?t=1761755501\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/6903894ef2f6f6daee4eaac2a44944de.webm?t=1761755501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/6903894ef2f6f6daee4eaac2a44944de.mp4?t=1761755501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/e22f539dd14bb48bd88a34c5e984c0e0.avif?t=1761755501\" width=365 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you find yourself in any danger, the <strong>GunShop</strong> is not responsible for any damage physical or psychological on workers, so be careful!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/a9ba553482d6e812db12840dbb76f433.poster.avif?t=1761755501\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/a9ba553482d6e812db12840dbb76f433.webm?t=1761755501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/a9ba553482d6e812db12840dbb76f433.mp4?t=1761755501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/c7e69698e46cd976d14a9dd3133bb297.avif?t=1761755501\" width=365 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Always finish your work on time, every shift has a deadline to deliver your work, the workers that choose not to deliver in time, <span class=\"bb_strike\">are all sent to him</span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/4c9b09f617a7e961f941e2a6280416e6.poster.avif?t=1761755501\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/4c9b09f617a7e961f941e2a6280416e6.webm?t=1761755501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/4c9b09f617a7e961f941e2a6280416e6.mp4?t=1761755501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262950/extras/3c279605e2e52efcfb345b7251a7b42a.avif?t=1761755501\" width=365 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is important to maintain communication with your coworkers, during meals every worker gathers at the cafeteria of the Gunshop to eat and socialize.</p>",
